# Indeterminate

⚠️ **Deprecation warning** ⚠️

This component has been deprecated and is no longer maintained. We recommend using the `Loader` package instead.

## Installation & Import

```bash
yarn add @ids-ts/indeterminate
```

```tsx
import { Indeterminate, IndeterminateLong, IndeterminateShort } from '@ids-ts/indeterminate';
```

