## Usage Patterns

### Indeterminate Long Spinner

```tsx
() => (
  <IndeterminateLong data-testid="shortIntuitSpinner" />
)
```

### Playground

```tsx
({ size, spinnerType })
```

### Showcase

```tsx
() => (
  <>
    <div>
      <h3>Indeterminate Long Spinner</h3>
      <IndeterminateLong
        data-testid="longIntuitSpinner"
        ariaLabel="indeterminate-long-spinner"
      />
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3>Indeterminate Short Spinner with size variation</h3>
      <IndeterminateShort
        size={64}
        data-testid="shortIntuitSpinner"
        ariaLabel="indeterminate-short-spinner"
      />
    </div>
  </>
)
```

